38:31.015 --> 38:32.516
The one in the orange shirt.

38:32.517 --> 38:33.725
That's the guy from the hospital.

38:33.726 --> 38:34.935
The one I thought looked nice.

38:34.936 --> 38:37.104
Honk-honk.

