40:04.609 --> 40:06.443
Guys, what is happening?

40:06.444 --> 40:08.445
We're all right!

40:08.446 --> 40:13.446
We're all right.

40:19.958 --> 40:21.917
- Almost there.
- I certainly hope so, darling,

40:21.918 --> 40:24.211
as much as I love
spending time with you.

40:24.212 --> 40:29.212
Aah!

40:36.474 --> 40:39.476
Tracy, I love you.

40:39.477 --> 40:41.270
All right! Open the door!

40:41.271 --> 40:45.607
Open up, Tony. Let's 99-

