46:51.641 --> 46:53.850
I'm sure you'd like to have it on tape.

46:53.851 --> 46:55.226
If it's not on camera,

46:55.227 --> 46:57.938
it's like it never happened, right?

46:57.939 --> 46:59.481
Okay, Jay, listen to me.

46:59.482 --> 47:02.317
I'm trying to get home
to my family, okay?

47:02.318 --> 47:04.235
