from anybody else.

47:15.247 --> 47:17.999
All that shit on the news
is a pack of lies.

47:18.000 --> 47:19.876
72,000 hits in eight minutes.

47:19.877 --> 47:21.878
- That's unbelievable.
- Congratulations. You're famous.

47:21.879 --> 47:23.588
