Yo, dude.

48:32.074 --> 48:33.867
Where are you, man?

48:33.868 --> 48:35.994
Ridley, yo back at you.

48:35.995 --> 48:38.038
We're in the middle
of fucking nowhere out here.

48:38.039 --> 48:39.080
How's Deb?

48:39.081 --> 48:41.124
Uh, she's okay.

48:41.125 --> 48:43.209
You know, coping.

48:43.210 --> 48:47.797
Look, if you need anything,
